Home / Shop / Cannabis Seeds / Feminized Seeds

Feminized seeds have undergone a process to produce only female plants. This means that every seed will produce a female cannabis plant, and it is the female plants that yield the marijuana flowers. Feminized seeds are a great choice for anyone who is after a single generation harvest. It is also a good choice for beginners in order to avoid the selection process.
